summary: “It’s too early and you are here, beautiful.” Peter was surprised when you entered into your first class of the morning. He shut...
caption:
“It’s too early and you are here, beautiful.” Peter was surprised when you entered into your first class of the morning. He shut down his laptop, perpahs he was watching some Youtube video. You rolled your eyes due to that nickname.

“Same as you. I had to fix some documents, what about you?” he shrugged his shoulders as you sat in the row next to him. You smiled and went back to your things, taking books out of your schoolbag.

“Have I told you how beautiful you look today?”

summary: a blurb abt spideychelle??
question: a blurb abt spideychelle??
answer:
blurb night - requests open

Let’s just imagine that Peter asked Michelle out for homecoming and both of them dancing together. I can say with confidence that Peter is an awful dancer and Michelle is like him just trying her best. And by them trying their best I mean that both of them just do not know what to do and just move around awkwardly. After a while, it eventually ends up in them jumping around and laughing so hard that their bodies hurt and they still do not really want to stop. Because even though they make complete fools out of themselves, they enjoy every minute of it.
